    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Walking and walking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember saying the soldiers that we had were not even SS.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were Ukrainians and Lithuanians soldiers, which joined the Nazi movement.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he says, whatever you got, give me a watch, whatever you got, because you're not going-- you don't-- they knew where we going.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we still don't-- we still don't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- I'm going to go to break now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
